5" alt="Riemann" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1787775)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/riemann" >Riemann</a></span></li> <li><em>The integration of SCP-5788 into the plumbing of the kitchen makes removal and characterisation difficult.</em></li> </ul> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">November 2020:</span></span></h4> <p><strong>1 November 2020 - selected by <em>cybersqyd</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/they-call-him-he-who-cannot-see-his-reflection">To The Dreams He Is No Nobody</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=637830&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180935" alt="SoullessSingularity" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=637830)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/soullesssingularity" >SoullessSingularity</a></span></li> <li><em>Suffice to say, Nobody and the dreams have something that humans may identify as a friendship.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 November 2020 - selected by <em>Dr Moned</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/catching-up">Catching Up</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4558017&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180935" alt="Grigori Karpin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4558017)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grigori-karpin" >Grigori Karpin</a></span></li> <li><em>“I know you and a group of MTF-Beta-777 went into an alternate reality. You ‘read’ a structure there and had what amounts to a psychotic break.”</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>17 November 2020 - selected by <em>Truc Linh</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/procedure-420-perinaldo">Procedure 420-Perinaldo</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppermint-legos" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5515758&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180935" alt="peppermint_legos" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5515758)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppermint-legos" >peppermint_legos</a></span></li> <li><em>My grandpa dodged Vietnam with a bari sax.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>25 November 2020 - selected by <em>caspian2</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5610">SCP-5610</a> (To Put a Cat on Your Head) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/veralta" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6030962&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180935" alt="Veralta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6030962)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/veralta" >Veralta</a></span></li> <li><em>Approximately 56 percent of Japan's population has been found to have an instance of SCP-5610 resting atop of their head.</em></li> </ul> <h4><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">December 2020:</span></span></h4> <p>No Reviewers' Spotlight features this month due to contest prize feature schedule. Happy Holidays!</p> </div> </div> </div> <hr /> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">2021&nbsp;REVIEWERS’&nbsp;SPOTLIGHT&nbsp;JANUARY&nbsp;-&nbsp;APRIL</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">2021&nbsp;REVIEWERS’&nbsp;SPOTLIGHT&nbsp;JANUARY&nbsp;-&nbsp;APRIL&nbsp;</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <h4><span><span 