ttp://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3754950)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/amelia-wright" >Amelia Wright</a></span></li> <li><em>As such, the O5 Council have ruled that SCP-5699 does not require active containment.</em></li> </ul> <p><strong>9 January 2021 - selected by <em>Quadraginta</em></strong></p> <ul> <li>Featured page: <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5266">SCP-5266</a> (IDIOT SUCCUMBS TO NEUROTOXIN WHILE LISTENING TO MACHO MAN CLICK NOW TO SEE) by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/iamtheooga" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3942052&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180935" alt="IAmTheOoga" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3942052)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/iamtheooga" >IAmTheOoga</a></span></li> <li><em>Object Class: Keter</em></li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> <hr /> <p>by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404533&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180935" alt="Zyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404533)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" >Zyn</a></span></p> 
