amp;timestamp=1610180939" alt="DrTesla" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2194347)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drtesla" >DrTesla</a></span>)<br /> <span style="text-decoration: underline;">Spanish to English</span><br /> <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/peligro-igniciervos">Danger: Incinideer!</a> (Original by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dc-yerko" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1780049&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180939" alt="Dc_Yerko" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1780049)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dc-yerko" >Dc_Yerko</a></span>)<br /> <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/doctor-muerte">Herman Fuller Presents: The Doctor of Death</a> (Original by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dc-yerko" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1780049&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180939" alt="Dc_Yerko" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1780049)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dc-yerko" >Dc_Yerko</a></span>)<br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> For my Spanish Author Page, click <a href="http://lafundacionscp.wikidot.com/ficha-de-uncle-nicolini">here</a>.<br /> For my INT Author Page, click <a href="http://scp-int.wikidot.com/nico-translation-page">here</a>.</p> </div> </div> </div> <br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span>my characters<br /> <div id="wiki-tabview-3ba2689441fd334a769db3355c00e645" class="yui-navset"> <ul class="yui-nav"> <li class="selected"><a href="javascript:;"><em>intro</em></a></li> <li><a href="javascript:;"><em>Dr. Everwood</em></a></li> <li><a href="javascript:;"><em>Faeowyn Wilson</em></a></li> </ul> <div class="yui-content"> <div id="wiki-tab-0-0"> <p>hello yes<br /> these are characters that I have created or have influenced the direction of greatly. though they aren't wildly popular, i figure i may as well include documentations of their appearances, personalities, traits, etc just in case you want to use one of them in your story/scp.</p> <p>also if i find out you lewded any of them i will go to your house and you will be very sorry</p> </div> <div id="wiki-tab-0-1" style="display:none"> <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">APPEARS IN</span></p> <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">SUMMARY</span><br /> Dr. Everwood is a bright and cheerful person, despite her appearance. She has short brown hair, green eyes, and looks tired most of the time. Is missing her right arm, which she lost in a [DATA EXPUNGED] incident. Doesn't like her prosthetic arm but wears it when necessary. Despite her snark and grump, she knows how to have fun and likes doing so. Identifies as female, but looks relatively androgynous and likes it that way. Born and raised in Florida. Speaks Spanish and English.</p> <p>You can use her as a GoI specialist if you like, as that's what she enjoys.<br /> Works for the UIU as a rookie agent in the Aces and Eights canon.<br /> Lead Dr. Wondertainment researcher in Wonderful World canon.<br /> Administrator in the canon of <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4224">SCP-4224</a></p> <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">HOW DOES SHE LIKE HER COFFEE?</span><br /> Prefers bubble tea, but if forced to drink coffee likes espresso with a little bit of sugar.<br /> <span style="text-decoration: underline;">HOW OFTEN DOES SHE SAY USE SWEARS</span><br /> Sometimes.</p> </div> <div id="wiki-tab-0-2" style="display:none"> <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">APPEARS IN</span></p> <p>LOVINGLY MADE WITH MY FRIEND AND PAL DARKSTUFF</p> <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">SUMMARY</span><br /> Faeowyn Wilson (born Felix Wilson) is Tim Wilson's daughter and the second person to run Wilson's Wildlife Solutions. She is very intelligent and inherited her father's love for animals, but is a lot more competent and responsible than him. Is a very 'no-nonsense' person. She is tan, has shoulder length hair, brown eyes, has an athletic body type, and is often seen wearing a WWS-embroidered khaki shirt and shorts. Smells of sunscreen. Is dating fellow WWS volunteer Alex Molina.<br /> Dislikes Marshall Carter and Dark.<br /> Is friends with Holly 'Wondertainment' Light in Wonderful World canon.<br /> Is aware of Three Portlands and the Wanderer's Library.</p> <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">HOW DOES SHE LIKE HER COFFEE?</span><br /> Pitch black.</p> <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">HOW OFTEN DOES SHE SWEAR?</span><br /> In front of her dad? Never. Elsewhere? depends on how angry she is.</p> </div> </div> </div> <div style="text-align: center;"> <h2><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">like my stuff?</span></span></h2> <p>aw shucks, thanks. i'm open for collabs almost all the time, so just hit me up. it helps if you have an idea though, so don't just come up to me asking to write.</p> <h2><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">srs bznz</span></span></h2> </div> <br /> in the event something happens to me and i disappear for 5 years or die, i leave all my non-colab articles entrusted to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aismallard" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4598089&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180939" alt="aismallard" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4598089)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aismallard" >aismallard</a></span>, and all my collab articles with the respective co-authors. The only exception to this is <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/moon-champion-s-cinco-de-mayo-extravaganza">moon champion's cinco de mayo extravaganza</a>, which would be left to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3187823&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180939" alt="CadaverCommander" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3187823)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" >CadaverCommander</a></span>.<img src="https://i.imgur.com/UEQWeKN.png" alt="UEQWeKN.png" class="image" /><br /> <span style="font-size:75%;">art by hawkguyy</span><br /> <img src="https://images-wixmp-ed30a86b8c4ca887773594c2.wixmp.com/f/7b1f27d5-18cb-401d-b26c-b485bd34c437/ddu82jt-d8fda1b7-679d-4f84-afbb-141ee270c7d9.png/v1/fill/w_894,h_894,q_70,strp/faeowynn_wilson___darius_by_uncertaintycrossing_ddu82jt-pre.jpg?token=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..DUwrASgCxpyhg49r5YoQ5bXj0otDUefMIf_IpvnVLl4" alt="faeowynn_wilson___darius_by_uncertaintycrossing_ddu82jt-pre.jpg?token=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..DUwrASgCxpyhg49r5YoQ5bXj0otDUefMIf_IpvnVLl4" class="image" /><br /> <span style="font-size:75%;">art by uncertaintycrossing</span><br /> <img src="https://usercontent.irccloud-cdn.com/file/JK1T92wL/Faeowynn.jpg" alt="Faeowynn.jpg" class="image" /><br /> <span style="font-size:75%;">art by dr merlin_VI</span><br /> <img src="https://usercontent.irccloud-cdn.com/file/xrsIOMYJ/20201225_140445.jpg" alt="20201225_140445.jpg" class="image" /><br /> <span style="font-size:75%;">art by uncertaintycrossing</span><br /> <img src="https://usercontent.irccloud-cdn.com/file/bI8nHySq/image0-2.png" alt="image0-2.png" class="image" /><br /> <span style="font-size:75%;">art by dr whitney</span></div> <p>by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180939" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" >Uncle Nicolini</a></span></p> 
