&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Special Containment Procedures:&lt;/strong&gt; SCP-5978 can be stored in any place. SCP-5978 is only allowed to be accessed by personnel with level 3 security clearance to prevent misapplication.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Description:&lt;/strong&gt; SCP-5978 was first found in an apartment basement by MTFs MTFs tested some of the abilities of the grater and found that it can grate the wood and marble and as these abilities are anomalies, they were taken to the SCP Foundation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SCP-5978 has a completely normal grated appearance Anomaly feature of SCP-5978: The person can grate everything, with this grater and cut it into small pieces. It can grate anything, but it is not known how it is still solid after grating so many hard things.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;No conclusion could be drawn when the planning parts of SCP-5978 were examined under microscopes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Test A - Date [DATA EXPUNGED]&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Subject: Test to SCP-5978&amp;#160;s limits of grating&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Procedure:Tryed to grate iron by SCP-5978&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Results:Grated&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Analysis: SCP-5978 can grate everything if can grate iron it can grate so many things&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
